(UPBEAT MUSIC)

05:00.834 --> 05:06.207
<i>♪ Yeah ♪</i>

05:06.208 --> 05:09.666
<i>♪ Yeah, yeah ♪</i>

05:09.667 --> 05:11.791
<i>♪ Yeah ♪</i>

05:11.792 --> 05:15.082
<i>♪ Mmm ♪</i>

05:15.083 --> 05:18.082
<i>♪ Yeah, yeah ♪</i>

05:18.083 --> 05:21.958
(MUSIC PLAYING)

05:21.959 --> 05:25.708
<i>♪ Ooh ooh ooh ♪</i>

